data.description:
This cozy 3 bed 2 bath on 1 acre is waiting for you! The living area is large with a high ceiling and wood beam running the length of the room.  The room is complimented by a beautiful stone fireplace.  Master bedroom is  oversized and can easily accommodate a workspace for a home office.  Out back just off the carport there is a large wood deck for cookouts and a covered front porch to relax on.  The detached garage has multi uses with one single door entrance but could easily handle two cars with the addition of an additional garage door or utilize the extra space for your own hobby or workshop.   The home is in need of some updates for your own DIY project.  Owner is currently disabled and the home is BEING SOLD AS IS.  No seller concessions!  NOTE LOCKBOX IS ON THE BACK DOOR DUE TO STEPS IN FRONT BEING REPAIRED-

PROFESSIONAL PHOTOS TO COME
